.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/logs/iter-018.err:12732:   137	| Gating | Flag off / manifest legacy ⇒ inert; both on ⇒ served | `resolve.cjs --hub … --prompt …` with `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING` on and off |
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/logs/iter-018.err:12746:    64	  - **Evidence**: `resolveRoute` returns null unless `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING=1` AND the manifest reads `servingAuthority: compiled`; the flag-off CLI prints the legacy sentinel `{servingAuthority: legacy, hubId}`.
