.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/logs/iter-009.err:60:- F-2-5 [benchmark/P2] Hub-type detection (isHubTypeSkill, run-skill-benchmark.cjs:68 keys on hub-router.json) is misaligned with compiled-serving eligibility (keys on activation manifest + advisor-recommend.ts COMPILED_ROUTING_HUBS allowlist). A hub can have --route-gold auto-on while compiled-parity is structurally N/A.
