.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/logs/iter-003.err:5786:.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/011-runtime-engine/spec.md:76:- Flipping all seven hubs' serving authority to `compiled` - [note] now **complete**: executed one-hub-at-a-time; all seven `010-live-activation` manifests read `servingAuthority: compiled`, each byte-exact-reversible via a retained `manifest.serving-prior.json`.
