.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/logs/iter-015.err:2998:.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/011-runtime-engine/checklist.md:52:  - **Evidence**: `compiled-route.cjs` routes through the child's archetype engine (`evaluateCanary` or `evaluateRoute`) over `loadSnapshot`; it defines no independent decision algebra.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/logs/iter-015.err:3001:.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/011-runtime-engine/checklist.md:64:  - **Evidence**: `resolveRoute` returns null unless `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING=1` AND the manifest reads `servingAuthority: compiled`; the flag-off CLI prints the legacy sentinel `{servingAuthority: legacy, hubId}`.
