.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/logs/iter-015.err:3939:   136	| REQ-005 | Integrate parity as a Lane C gate without changing D1-D5. | `report.compiledRouting` contains mode, eligible rows, parity counts, drift rows, breakages, and frozen hashes; routing divergence or breakage produces a distinct blocked verdict and non-zero exit, while drift remains visibly classified according to the authoritative contract. |
