xt:v1.5`. The cascade auto-detects Ollama and persists nomic-embed-text-v1.5 (768d) as the active embedder — no API keys, all-local.'), ('_NOTE_RETRY_TUNING', 'Bulk re-embed retry tuning: raised pending cap + max-age + faster batch/interval so a large embedding backlog drains instead of being parked as failed (defaults park excess/old pending: cap 1000, 24h age, 5-per-5min).'), ('_NOTE_SOCKET', 'macOS sun_path limit (104 chars): the default bridge socket path under database/daemon-ipc.sock exceeds the limit and the launcher fails with EINVAL. Pin to a short /tmp path so the multi-client bridge can bind.')]\n.codex/config.toml mk_skill_advisor [('HF_EMBED_SERVER_URL', 'unix:///tmp/mk-hf-embed/hf-embed.sock'), ('MK_SKILL_ADVISOR_DB_DIR', '.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/database'), ('MK_SKILL_ADVISOR_HOOK_DISABLED', '0'), ('MK_SKILL_ADVISOR_TRUST_DEFAULT', 'trusted'), ('SPECKIT_ADVISOR_DOC_TRIGGERS', 'true'), ('SPECKIT_IPC_SOCKET_DIR', '/tmp/mk-skill-advisor'), ('SPECKIT_MAX_SECONDARY_CLIENTS', '64'), ('_NOTE_1_DB', 'Database lives at .opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/database/skill-graph.sqlite by default; MK_SKILL_ADVISOR_DB_DIR overrides, with SYSTEM_SKILL_ADVISOR_DB_DIR as a legacy fallback (both still recognized by the launcher + handlers).'), ('_NOTE_3_THRESHOLDS', 'Advisor confidence/uncertainty thresholds are tunable: SPECKIT_ADVISOR_CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD (default 0.8), SPECKIT_ADVISOR_UNCERTAINTY_THRESHOLD (default 0.35). Lane weights tunable via SPECKIT_ADVISOR_LANE_WEIGHTS_JSON + SPECKIT_ADVISOR_LANE_SHADOW_WEIGHTS_JSON (partial-merge JSON, post-022/011/4b).'), ('_NOTE_DOC_TRIGGERS', 'Opt-in doc-frontmatter harvest: skill_graph_scan ingests references/assets trigger_phrases into skill_docs and advisor_recommend returns matchedDocs pointers (dampened derived-lane signal). Default-off in code; enabled for this repo. Unset/false to roll back.'), ('_NOTE_HF_EMBED_SOCKET', \"Shared hf-local model-server socket — identical to mk-spe