.opencode/specs/system-skill-advisor/z_archive/009-playbook-run-and-remediation/005-finding-remediation/research/prompts/iteration-4.codexlog:2821:.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/database/README.md:23:Runtime state belongs to the standalone advisor package. Tests may override the directory with `MK_SKILL_ADVISOR_DB_DIR`; `SYSTEM_SKILL_ADVISOR_DB_DIR` remains a legacy fallback. Operator documentation should treat the package-local path as canonical.
