   193	| Parity | Compiled versus legacy route-gold outcomes | Frozen Lane C scorer consumed read-only; normalized routing equality |
   194	| Canary | One environment profile only | Profile matrix proving the repository default remains off |
   195	| Rollback | Per-hub authority and fleet kill-switch | Prior-manifest restore plus `=0` legacy-serving proof |
   196	| Integrity | Frozen scorer pin | SHA-256 before and after every migration stage |
