   128	| Runtime implementation tests | Planned; no runtime implementation exists in this phase |
   129	| Route-gold compiled-versus-legacy parity | Planned for the benchmark-alignment phase |
   130	| Drift CI and status readout | Planned for P0-P1 |
   131	| Canary and kill-switch drill | Planned for P2 and P4 |
   132	| Frozen scorer digest comparison | Planned per stage |
