   191	
   192	<!-- ANCHOR:edge-cases -->
   193	## L2: EDGE CASES
   194	
   195	### Generator Input
   196	
   197	- `--compiled-routing ready` with `--kind standalone`: reject with an actionable parent-only error.
   198	- Unknown compiled state: reject before writing a success result.
   199	- Existing target folder: preserve the current refusal; do not mint against an ambiguous target.
   200	
   201	### Manifest Outcomes
   202	
   203	- Canonical minter unavailable: non-zero result; no compiled-ready claim.
   204	- Minter returns a path outside the canonical store: reject through the shared validator.
   205	- Manifest exists but live inputs changed before verification: stale result; report re-mint required.
   206	- Legacy selection with a pre-existing manifest at the target identity: halt and require an explicit reconciliation decision rather than silently deleting or reusing it.
   207	
   208	### Template Integrity
   209	
   210	- Hub name substitution must occur in the CLI command and closing sentence.
   211	- The directive must precede, not replace, the prose router.
   212	<!-- /ANCHOR:edge-cases -->
