    20	//   3. Migrating to TS would require either (a) building this file into the
    21	//      same dist tree the plugin watches, creating a chicken-and-egg with
    22	//      cache-signature freshness, or (b) maintaining a
    23	//      .ts → .mjs build step exclusive to this single file. Either path is
    24	//      a larger packet than the source/dist boundary fixes here.
    25	//
    26	// Smoke tests asserting the subprocess envelope live in the standalone
